I have a Nokia bluetooth headset BH-105,and a bluetooth usb dongle. And I want to connect them together. Following are the steps.
###Software Preparation On ArchLinux, Install &ldquo;bluez&rdquo; and &ldquo;bluez-utils&rdquo;
	$ sudo pacman -S bluez bluez-utils $ sudo systemctl start bluetooth &amp;&amp; sudo systemctl enable bluetooth
